ENV LC_ALL=C.UTF-8

RUN apt-get -y upgrade
RUN apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install wget python3-dev git python3-venv python3-pip python-is-python3
RUN apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install build-essential tcl

RUN apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install unrar

RUN apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install apparmor-utils

RUN sed '/^profile libreoffice-soffice \/usr\/lib\/libreoffice\/program\/soffice.bin/a owner @{HOME}\/pandora\/tasks\/\*\* rwk,/' /etc/apparmor.d/usr.lib.libreoffice.program.soffice.bin -i

RUN pip3 install --no-cache-dir poetry

WORKDIR pandora

COPY pandora pandora/
COPY tools tools/
COPY bin bin/
COPY doc doc/
COPY website website/
COPY pyproject.toml .
COPY poetry.lock .
COPY README.md .
COPY LICENSE .

RUN echo PANDORA_HOME="`pwd`" >> .env
RUN poetry install
RUN poetry run tools/3rdparty.py
